OL,3,CRats spotted roaming around Ysbyty
OL,4,CGlan Clwyd
OL,6,FRats have reportedly been seen roaming
OL,7,Faround a North Wales hospital after
OL,8,Fchewing through foam in the walls.
OL,10,FBetsi Cadwaladr University Health
OL,11,FBoard has admitted that the rodents
OL,12,Fhave been spotted at Ysbyty Glan Clwyd
OL,13,Fin Bodelwyddan.
OL,15,FSightings of the rodents were reported
OL,16,Fin the Ivor Lewis building, a pre-
OL,17,Foperative assessment clinic attended
OL,18,Fby patients before surgery.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
