OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772647565
OL,3,CRats spotted roaming around Ysbyty
OL,4,CGlan Clwyd
OL,6,FThe building is at the front of the
OL,7,Fhospital, adjacent to the main
OL,8,Fentrance.
OL,10,FRhyl councillor Brian Jones said the
OL,11,Fsituation was was "totally
OL,12,Funacceptable". He added: "Whilst
OL,13,Faccepting the fact that vermin, in
OL,14,Fparticular rats, are a common problem
OL,15,Fin all aspects of life ` and we know
OL,16,Fhow rats are, and we are always close
OL,17,Fto a rat ` but to hear this in a
OL,18,Fsetting like Glan Clwyd, it is very
OL,19,Fconcerning.
OL,26,@sD@SOUtD@MO]tD@ZOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
