FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772647565
OL,3,CRats spotted roaming around Ysbyty
OL,4,CGlan Clwyd
OL,6,FHe added: "If I were a patient, I'm
OL,7,Fnot personally frightened of rats, but
OL,8,FI know people who would be absolutely
OL,9,Fpetrified to hear there is an issue
OL,10,Fwith a rat infestation at Glan Clwyd
OL,11,FHospital. I know people who probably
OL,12,Fwouldn't attend, and if they were in
OL,13,Fthere and heard this, they'd be
OL,14,Flooking to get out asap, regardless of
OL,15,Ftheir condition."
OL,17,FThe health board says it has taken
OL,18,Fpest control measures and insists
OL,19,Fthere is "no evidence of an
OL,20,Finfestation".
OL,26,@nD@KOUwD@QO]{D@JOU|D@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
