PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772647565
OL,3,CRats spotted roaming around Ysbyty
OL,4,CGlan Clwyd
OL,6,FStuart Keen, the board's director of
OL,7,Fenvironment and estates, said: "There
OL,8,Fhave been a small number of rat
OL,9,Fsightings inside the Ivor Lewis
OL,10,Fbuilding of the hospital.
OL,12,F"We have established pest control
OL,13,Fmeasures in place across the site,
OL,14,Fincluding routine inspections and
OL,15,Fmonitoring. In this instance, rodents
OL,16,Fhave chewed through some foam used to
OL,17,Fseal around pipe entry points,
OL,18,Fcreating small gaps.
OL,26,@oD@`OUtD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
