OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772647565
OL,3,CRats spotted roaming around Ysbyty
OL,4,CGlan Clwyd
OL,6,F"As soon as this was identified, we
OL,7,Fundertook a thorough review of the
OL,8,Fbuilding. We checked the external
OL,9,Fperimeter to ensure the main barriers
OL,10,Fremain intact and audited all ground
OL,11,Ffloor rooms to inspect where pipes
OL,12,Fenter the building. This identified a
OL,13,Flimited number of areas where sealing
OL,14,Fneeded to be reinforced."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
