PN,46606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772647565
OL,3,CRats spotted roaming around Ysbyty
OL,4,CGlan Clwyd
OL,6,F"A maintenance contractor has been
OL,7,Farranged to seal these gaps, and
OL,8,Fenhanced monitoring is now in place
OL,9,Fwith our specialist pest control
OL,10,Fproviders. This is a building
OL,11,Fmaintenance issue that is being
OL,12,Faddressed promptly, and there is no
OL,13,Fimpact on patient care or clinical
OL,14,Fservices."
