OL,3,CRats spotted roaming around Ysbyty
OL,4,CGlan Clwyd
OL,6,FHe added: "Large hospital sites,
OL,7,Fparticularly those in rural locations
OL,8,Fsurrounded by open land, can
OL,9,Foccasionally experience pest nuisance
OL,10,Fdespite preventative measures. We have
OL,11,Fclear procedures to manage this
OL,12,Fswiftly when it occurs."
